16 and construct state-of-the-art facilities that will open the door for local business opportunities
17 and job creation in the motion picture and television industry; and
18 WHEREAS, Mr. Perry strongly supports our state and national communities through
19 charities such as Feeding America, Covenant House, Hosea Feed the Hungry, Project
20 Adventure, Perry Place, and his own foundation, the Tyler Perry Foundation, which
21 transforms tragedy into triumph by empowering economically disadvantaged youths, seniors,
22 and families to overcome adversity by achieving a better quality of life; and
23 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this remarkable and distinguished
24 Georgian be recognized appropriately by dedicating a road in his honor.
25 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED AND ENACTED BY THE GENERAL
26 ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA that the portion of State Route 92 from Interstate 20 to
27 Riverside Parkway in Douglas County is dedicated as the Perry Parkway.
28 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Department of Transportation is authorized and
29 directed to erect and maintain appropriate signs dedicating the Perry Parkway.
30 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
31 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to Mr. Tyler Perry and
32 to the Department of Transportation.
